modName: Sir. Rodney Longbars Big Book of Cheats - Nexus Edition
summary: Hello, I am Ceranoe, formerly known as Sir. Rodney Longbar. This is my cheat/guide modification to skyrim that adds a set of 10 custom selections under the help menu.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a specially designed (yet slightly unorganized) set of help menu items listing from 1-10 containing all of the console commands, item id codes and small instructions on how to use them. I have personally taken all of this information from the skyrim wiki website, and compact it for easy use.

NOTE: This is not compatible with SKYUI

NOTE: If not all of the console commands are working/up to date, please let me know which command and/or id code is false and i shall correct it and even place your name in a credit function.

NOTE: If there is enough demand, I shall make an abriged edition containing only mainstream cheats, and a compact edition being more organized and easier to use.
author: Ceranoe
